1. *Maja* je danas otišla u prodavnicu. (*Maja* went to the store today.)
2. Čuli smo da će *Maja* dobiti unapređenje na poslu. (We heard that *Maja* will get a promotion at work.)
3. *Majo*, hoćeš li večeras ići sa nama u bioskop? (*Maja*, do you want to come to the cinema with us tonight?)
4. Naš pas se zove *Majka*, ali mi je skraćujemo na *Maja*. (Our dog's name is *Majka*, but we shorten it to *Maja*.)
5. Prošle godine sam provela *Majine* rođendanske poklone. (Last year, I wrapped *Maja's* birthday presents.)
6. *Maji* se sviđa da čita knjige. (*Maja* likes to read books.)
7. Danas sam kupio *majin* poklon za Dan žena. (Today, I bought *Maja's* gift for International Women's Day.)
8. Na *Majinom* licu se videla sreća kada je primila poklon. (Happiness was visible on *Maja's* face when she received the gift.)
9. U mom kraju ima jedna prodavnica koja se zove "Majin kutak". (There's a store in my neighborhood called "Maja's Corner".)
10. *Majino* ime je vrlo popularno u Srbiji. (*Maja's* name is very popular in Serbia.)